  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342960/extras/48f0dfed6a20489854625d9677672572.webp?t=1759219736\" width=144 height=52 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Due to an experiment failure, a machine explodes and causes all humans to turn into bunnies. The protagonist, Gunner Bunny, must investigate and find out who is behind this matter, and the disappearance of his wife, Fire Lily!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342960/extras/85754806d9146386ac4e3df12f3dd15d.avif?t=1759219736\" width=228 height=76 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342960/extras/540364035af506fadb2e253479c4d160.webp?t=1759219736\" width=163 height=46 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Blaster Bunny Redemption</strong> is the first game of \"The Princess Trilogy\", a classic action platform game. Choose a level, jump, kill enemies and finally defeat the boss to move forward. And is a reboot of the original <strong>Blaster Bunny +</strong>, changing the story to match its two sequels, BB Chronicles and BB Sacrilege.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342960/extras/f545bc65e66343ab9c2ea7f827987cf9.avif?t=1759219736\" width=208 height=76 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342960/extras/cf29e9d1c224bdee19b03820944c746f.webp?t=1759219736\" width=232 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 Stages.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 Bosses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 Secret Items.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Big Lore & Long Cutscenes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Cinema to see the cinematics again.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn Medals by completing levels quickly and without dying.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 Languages (English and Spanish)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assist Mode.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342960/extras/f6a51870b374ee7eb69bde25a1fbb8e0.webp?t=1759219736\" width=172 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342960/extras/c4386a915a6e3b6b2e571509ddba1d89.webp?t=1759219736\" width=304 height=46 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The soundtrack is created by <strong>Sweep Blast Studios</strong>.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342960/extras/48f0dfed6a20489854625d9677672572.webp?t=1759219736\" width=144 height=52 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Due to an experiment failure, a machine explodes and causes all humans to turn into bunnies. The protagonist, Gunner Bunny, must investigate and find out who is behind this matter, and the disappearance of his wife, Fire Lily!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342960/extras/85754806d9146386ac4e3df12f3dd15d.avif?t=1759219736\" width=228 height=76 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342960/extras/540364035af506fadb2e253479c4d160.webp?t=1759219736\" width=163 height=46 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Blaster Bunny Redemption</strong> is the first game of \"The Princess Trilogy\", a classic action platform game. Choose a level, jump, kill enemies and finally defeat the boss to move forward. And is a reboot of the original <strong>Blaster Bunny +</strong>, changing the story to match its two sequels, BB Chronicles and BB Sacrilege.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342960/extras/f545bc65e66343ab9c2ea7f827987cf9.avif?t=1759219736\" width=208 height=76 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342960/extras/cf29e9d1c224bdee19b03820944c746f.webp?t=1759219736\" width=232 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 Stages.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 Bosses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 Secret Items.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Big Lore & Long Cutscenes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Cinema to see the cinematics again.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn Medals by completing levels quickly and without dying.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 Languages (English and Spanish)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assist Mode.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342960/extras/f6a51870b374ee7eb69bde25a1fbb8e0.webp?t=1759219736\" width=172 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342960/extras/c4386a915a6e3b6b2e571509ddba1d89.webp?t=1759219736\" width=304 height=46 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The soundtrack is created by <strong>Sweep Blast Studios</strong>.</p>",
